dct_description_sm: Coordinates approximate and based on Greenwich meridian.
Shows topography, drainage, travel routes, places of historical interest.
Features illustrations of settlements, people, and domestic animals.
Descriptive text in a decorative cartouche: Appellationes nominum priscae & recentiores.
Appears in Ptolemaeus, Claudius, Geographia, (Basileae: Per Henricum Petrum, 1545). This atlas is a reprint of Münster's 1540 and 1542 editions.
